{"tid":1455392,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"開始覺得叫人唔好走個d先係鬼","createTime":"2019-08-12T08:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:10:47.000Z","uid":202804,"like":47,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6b6b613fa7df63a80db1329391df1435e1f8190f","tid":1455392,"uid":202804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:58:28.000Z","msg":"機場已經全部機取消左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身既目的已經達成<br />\n引起國際注意同癱瘓機場<br />\n<br />\n咁依家留守有咩作用?<br />\n如果要繼續癱瘓點解唔聽日再吹雞入去?<br />\n就算今晚留守到今晚12點, 個機場都係咁樣癱瘓法, 唔會有再大效果<br />\n唔同普通阻街路, 阻街路你要一大班人守住先可以封實條路<br />\n<br />\n但依家機場散..機場都唔會正常運作返<br />\n無必要增加自己既風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家自己去衡量下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好撚多鬼..都唔知自己咁稔係咪岩, 大家稔到d咩講出黎集思下"},{"pid":"4e2dd97a2530a9457d7476fca5c32a39d87414f7","tid":1455392,"uid":202804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:03:08.000Z","msg":"琴日咁既環境  如果有狗混入去搞事<br />\n就有哂藉口暴力清場<br />\n我係擔心呢樣"},{"pid":"9cc0551f40960cc6b7ab67fc8965b19198633c96","tid":1455392,"uid":202804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:08:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b1184e8a8926936e860403900117fe46dd605e9","tid":1455392,"uid":202804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:23:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"887ca0684bc6c87a09e381eecfc35ed055ac16c2","tid":1455392,"uid":237300,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:24:52.000Z","msg":"走走走，不受傷不被捕"},{"pid":"b742af9b2a7156c44d890f5d393bd1c97fa14393","tid":1455392,"uid":202804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:25:23.000Z","msg":"好撚多鬼丫  自己要識判斷<br />\n我無話自己一定岩<br />\n但班黑警仆街死啦"},{"pid":"3e5eecc058fd581f7893994f6c0a65496d7360f8","tid":1455392,"uid":202804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:27:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dfde1617ba9dc133cac0580d1e6d4884e9bb84e0","tid":1455392,"uid":20280